@host = http://localhost:9090

# ============================================================
# DTO Validation 검증 시나리오
#
# 검증 대상:
#   - Bean Validation (NotNull, PositiveOrZero) 위반 → 400
#   - LocalDateTime parse 실패 → 400
#   - 필수 query parameter 누락 → 400
#
# 사용법:
#   - 시나리오 각자 독립 (DB 상태 무관, 사전 등록 불필요)
#   - 모든 시나리오 응답은 400 기대
#   - 응답 본문 코드는 GlobalExceptionHandler 매핑 결과 (BAD_REQUEST 또는 enum 이름)
# ============================================================


# ============================================================
# [등록] 필수 필드 누락 / 잘못된 값
# ============================================================

### V01 courseId 누락 → 400
POST {{host}}/api/sales
Content-Type: application/json

{ "studentId": 9201, "paymentAmount": 49000, "paidAt": "2026-05-23T10:00:00" }

### V02 studentId 누락 → 400
POST {{host}}/api/sales
Content-Type: application/json

{ "courseId": 1, "paymentAmount": 49000, "paidAt": "2026-05-23T10:00:00" }

### V03 paymentAmount 누락 → 400
POST {{host}}/api/sales
Content-Type: application/json

{ "courseId": 1, "studentId": 9201, "paidAt": "2026-05-23T10:00:00" }

### V04 paidAt 누락 → 400
POST {{host}}/api/sales
Content-Type: application/json

{ "courseId": 1, "studentId": 9201, "paymentAmount": 49000 }

### V05 paymentAmount 음수 → 400 (PositiveOrZero 위반)
POST {{host}}/api/sales
Content-Type: application/json

{ "courseId": 1, "studentId": 9201, "paymentAmount": -1000, "paidAt": "2026-05-23T10:00:00" }

### V06 paidAt 잘못된 형식 → 400 (LocalDateTime parse 실패)
POST {{host}}/api/sales
Content-Type: application/json

{ "courseId": 1, "studentId": 9201, "paymentAmount": 49000, "paidAt": "2026-13-45T25:99:99" }

### V07 모든 필수 필드 누락 → 400
POST {{host}}/api/sales
Content-Type: application/json

{}


### [환불] 필수 필드 누락 / 잘못된 값

### V08 salesRecordId 누락 → 400
POST {{host}}/api/sales/cancellations
Content-Type: application/json

{ "refundAmount": 10000, "cancelledAt": "2026-05-23T10:00:00" }

### V09 refundAmount 누락 → 400
POST {{host}}/api/sales/cancellations
Content-Type: application/json

{ "salesRecordId": 1, "cancelledAt": "2026-05-23T10:00:00" }

### V10 cancelledAt 누락 → 400
POST {{host}}/api/sales/cancellations
Content-Type: application/json

{ "salesRecordId": 1, "refundAmount": 10000 }

### V11 refundAmount 음수 → 400 (PositiveOrZero 위반)
POST {{host}}/api/sales/cancellations
Content-Type: application/json

{ "salesRecordId": 1, "refundAmount": -1000, "cancelledAt": "2026-05-23T10:00:00" }

### V12 cancelledAt 잘못된 형식 → 400
POST {{host}}/api/sales/cancellations
Content-Type: application/json

{ "salesRecordId": 1, "refundAmount": 10000, "cancelledAt": "yesterday" }


### [조회] 필수 query parameter 누락 / 형식

### V13 from 누락 → 400
GET {{host}}/api/sales?toExclusive=2026-06-01T00:00:00

### V14 toExclusive 누락 → 400
GET {{host}}/api/sales?from=2026-05-01T00:00:00

### V15 from/toExclusive 둘 다 누락 → 400
GET {{host}}/api/sales

### V16 from 잘못된 날짜 형식 → 400
GET {{host}}/api/sales?from=invalid-date&toExclusive=2026-06-01T00:00:00

### V17 creatorId 잘못된 타입 (숫자 아님) → 400
GET {{host}}/api/sales?creatorId=abc&from=2026-05-01T00:00:00&toExclusive=2026-06-01T00:00:00
